data.description: Great Two Family brick House in a prime location at Brownsville. This property is well maintained by the owner and the property's current layout is: 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathroom on the 1st floor. The Second Floor also has the same features: 3 bed and 2 bathroom. The property has a big backyard and an ample side driveway with parking space that could fit up to 5 cars. Near you will have groceries, laundromats, and all mean of transportation. The property will be delivered fully vacant.
